Visited this newly reopened outlet recently and tried quite a few new items that I had never tried before!
They launched the all-new Tater Tots range in Plain/ Kimchi/ Seaweed flavours, as well as Cheesy Loaded Tots just for this outlet! So addictive that I wanted to keep on munching even though I was very full!
And I didnâ€™t know they had maki! So delicious!
Also stoked to try their new Banana Choco Balls, such an indulgent treat!
Of course their wings and drumlets were as tasty as I remembered!

4Fingers reopen in Jurong Point and launched some exclusive Limited Time offers at Jurong Point, including New Tater Tots in Plain, Kimchi, or Seaweed flavours, and Cheesy Loaded Tots!! Is a good crispy yummy offer.  Available a-la-carte or combo with a Coke and get a complimentary cosy Coke fleece pouch!!

I also get their signature Spicy Wingettes and Drumettes and Rendang Chicken
Very questionable serving size really. Pictures speak it all. Boneless chicken as thin as paper, cheesy loaded fries loaded w real estate.
